com.github.wuic.engine.impl.ehcache
Interface WuicEhcacheProvider

All Superinterfaces:
CacheProvider<Cache>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultEhCacheProvider
public interface WuicEhcacheProvider
extends CacheProvider<Cache>

This interface defines an object which provides a Cache from EHCache framework. Applications based on WUIC can defines through their wuic.xml configuration path their own implementation of this interface.

This interface as been designed to allow WUIC framework to not systematically the ehcache.xml path to retrieve a cache.
